      "name": "Note: When Chat Message Received"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Required Fields Present?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.query }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Frame the Assignment · ②→ Abort — Malformed Input",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -6,
        520
      ],
      "id": "27ddb227-1201-f53d-0c5b-dcd5c157d476",
      "name": "Note: Required Fields Present?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Abort — Malformed Input\n\nFails fast with a clear message; triggers the error workflow instead of processing bad data.",
