      "name": "Note: Frame the Assignment"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Coordinator Agent\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Unpack Sections · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail",
        "width": 280,
